Mass Effect is a registered trademark of EA INTERNATIONAL (STUDIO&#10; AND PUBLISHING) LTD. This program has no affiliation with BioWare&#10; or Electronic Arts."/>
                        </StackPanel>
                    </Grid>
                </ScrollViewer>
            </TabItem>
        </TabControl>
    </DockPanel>
</Controls:MetroWindow>
